# TestGen

Use the local `testgen` CLI when generating, improving, or validating tests.

Safe default flow:

```bash
testgen doctor --path=. --output-format json
testgen cost --path=./src --output-format json
testgen generate --path=./src --recursive --type=unit --dry-run --emit-patch --report-usage --output-format json
```

Write only after reviewing the dry-run patch or when the user explicitly asks.
